'''米克·積遜'''（{{lang-en|Mick Jackson}}，1943年10月4日－）是一名[[英国|英国]]电视和电影导演、制片人。他导演的著名电影有1992年的爱情片《[[保镖_(电影)|保镖]]》和1997年的灾难片《[[活火熔城|活火熔城]]》。2010年他导演的电影 ''Temple Grandin'' 为他赢得了[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]独立导演奖。

==部分作品==

=== 电视 ===
其中包括[[电视电影|电视电影]]：
* ''Connections'' (1978), a 10-part documentary series created with science historian [[James_Burke|James Burke]]
* The 1984 [[docufiction|docufiction]] ''[[Threads|Threads]]'', with [[Karen_Meagher|Karen Meagher]] and [[Reece_Dinsdale|Reece Dinsdale]].
* The 1987 文献电视片 ''Life Story'', with [[Jeff_Goldblum|Jeff Goldblum]] and [[Tim_Pigott-Smith|Tim Pigott-Smith]]
* The 1988 adaptation by [[Alan_Plater|Alan Plater]] of [[Chris_Mullin_(politician)|Chris Mullin]]'s 1982 novel ''[[A_Very_British_Coup|A Very British Coup]]'', with [[Ray_McAnally|Ray McAnally]]
* The 1995 文献电视片 ''[[Indictment:_The_McMartin_Trial|Indictment: The McMartin Trial]]''
* The 1999 adaptation of [[Mitch_Albom|Mitch Albom]]'s 1997 novel ''[[Tuesdays_with_Morrie|Tuesdays with Morrie]]'', with [[Jack_Lemmon|Jack Lemmon]]
* The 2002 HBO Special adaptation of Robert Wiener's non-fiction ''[[Live_from_Baghdad|Live from Baghdad]]'', with [[Michael_Keaton|Michael Keaton]] and [[Helena_Bonham_Carter|Helena Bonham Carter]]
* ''[[Covert_One:_The_Hades_Factor|Covert One: The Hades Factor]]'' (2006), a CBS miniseries based on the novel by [[Robert_Ludlum|Robert Ludlum]] and [[Gayle_Lynds|Gayle Lynds]]
* ''Temple Grandin'' (2010), [[HBO|HBO]]传记电影，[[Claire_Danes|Claire Danes]], [[Catherine_O'Hara|Catherine O'Hara]] 和  [[Julia_Ormond|Julia Ormond]]主演。

=== 电影 ===
* 1989年 ''Chattahoochee'', with [[Gary_Oldman|Gary Oldman]] 和 [[Dennis_Hopper|Dennis Hopper]]
* 1991年 ''L.A. Story'', with [[Steve_Martin|Steve Martin]].
* 1992年 [[保镖_(电影)|保镖]]/''The Bodyguard'', [[Whitney_Houston|Whitney Houston]] 与 [[凯文·科斯特纳|凯文·科斯特纳]]主演。
* 1994年 ''Clean Slate'', [[Dana_Carvey|Dana Carvey]] 与 [[Valeria_Golino|Valeria Golino]]主演。
* 1997年 [[活火熔城|活火熔城]]/''Volcano'', with [[Tommy_Lee_Jones|Tommy Lee Jones]] 和 [[Anne_Heche|Anne Heche]].

